1.0.name: wordpress/profiless
1.0.description: This plugin is very simple! It removes the menu icon to access the profile page for the selected user roles in wordpress admin pannel. It also redirects the locked user to the admin homepage if it tries to access directly the profile page (as the menuitem has been removed).
